cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper is about extending the attention mechanism for speech recognition, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with sequence generation and machine learning, which are covered by cs.SD (Systems and Control) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves deep learning techniques, which are covered by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
